data.description: Affordable and spacious home in the village of Centerburg.  This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home sits close to the town shops and Heart of Ohio trail.  The main level has a large living room, dining room, full bath and kitchen with room for a small breakfast table.  The 1 car garage has been converted into a great room perfect for entertaining.  All three bedrooms are upstairs plus the half bath.  The back porch steps out to a nice back deck perfect for grilling and chilling.  Fenced backyard and a storage shed for extra storage.  Plenty of parking space off the alley.
